  'Generate photorealistic product shots optimised for Midjourney v6 with specific camera settings, lighting rigs, and post-processing parameters. Perfect for DTC brands needing hero images.',
  E'Create a cinematic product photograph of {product_name} for a {brand_aesthetic} brand.\n\n**CAMERA SETUP:**\n- Camera: Phase One IQ4 150MP equivalent\n- Lens: {focal_length}mm prime, f/{aperture}\n- ISO: 50, Shutter: 1/125s\n- Aspect ratio: {aspect_ratio}\n\n**LIGHTING RIG:**\n- Key light: {key_light_type} at 45Â° camera-left, {key_light_modifier}\n- Fill: Negative fill (black V-flat) camera-right for dramatic shadow\n- Rim/hair light: Strip softbox 3/4 behind subject\n- Background: {background_description}\n\n**PRODUCT STYLING:**\n- Surface: {surface_material} with {surface_detail}\n- Props: {props_list}\n- Product angle: {camera_angle}\n- Hero detail to emphasise: {hero_detail}\n\n**POST-PROCESSING:**\n- Color grading: {color_grade_style}\n- Contrast: Medium-high\n- Skin/surface detail: Ultra-sharp with micro-contrast\n\n**NEGATIVE PROMPT:** No text, no watermarks, no blurry edges, no plastic look, no oversaturation\n\n--v 6.1 --ar {aspect_ratio} --style raw --s 250 --q 2',
