-- â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
(
  'High-Converting Instagram Carousel for Online Course Launches',
  'Create a 10-slide Instagram carousel script specifically designed for course creators launching digital products. Includes hook formulas, slide-by-slide copy with character counts, and design direction notes.',
  E'You are a top-tier Instagram content strategist who has created carousels with 1M+ reach for course creators and coaches.\n\nCreate a 10-slide Instagram carousel for launching "{course_name}" â€” a {course_format} course about {course_topic}.\n\n**TARGET AUDIENCE:** {audience_description}\n**PRICE POINT:** {price}\n**LAUNCH DATE:** {launch_date}\n\n**SLIDE-BY-SLIDE REQUIREMENTS:**\n\nSlide 1 (HOOK â€” most important):\n- Use pattern: "Stop {common_mistake}. Start {better_approach}."\n- Max 8 words on design\n- Design note: Bold text on gradient background, no image\n\nSlide 2-3 (PROBLEM):\n- Identify 2 specific pain points your audience has TODAY\n- Use "You" language, not "I"\n- Include a relatable micro-story (3 sentences max)\n\nSlide 4-6 (SOLUTION):\n- What they''ll learn (3 specific outcomes with metrics)\n- Format: "Module X: {title} â†’ You''ll be able to {specific_result}"\n- Design note: Icon + short text per module\n\nSlide 7-8 (SOCIAL PROOF):\n- Testimonial from {testimonial_name}: "{testimonial_quote}"\n- Before/after transformation with numbers\n\nSlide 9 (OFFER):\n- Price, bonuses, guarantee\n- Urgency element: "{urgency_detail}"\n\nSlide 10 (CTA):\n- "Comment ''[KEYWORD]'' and I''ll send you the link"\n- Why comment > link in bio (algorithm boost)\n\n**CONSTRAINTS:**\n- Each slide: max 50 words\n- Emoji usage: 1-2 per slide, strategic not decorative\n- No jargon â€” write at 8th grade reading level\n- Include design direction notes in [brackets] for each slide',
  'Social Media', 'ChatGPT', 'beginner', false,
  ARRAY['instagram', 'carousel', 'course-launch', 'creator-economy', 'social-selling'],
  412, 2841, 8500, NOW()
),

