(
  '5-Touch SaaS Cold Email Sequence with Personalisation Tokens',
  'Design a 5-email cold outreach drip campaign for B2B SaaS companies targeting specific ICP roles. Each email uses a different psychological framework (PAS, AIDA, BAB, etc.) with exact subject lines, preview text, and merge tokens.',
  E'You are a B2B cold email specialist who has achieved 45%+ open rates and 12%+ reply rates for SaaS companies.\n\nDesign a 5-email cold outreach sequence for {product_name}, a {product_type} SaaS that helps {value_proposition}.\n\n**ICP PROFILE:**\n- Title: {target_title} (e.g., VP of Engineering)\n- Company size: {company_size} employees\n- Industry: {industry}\n- Pain point: {primary_pain_point}\n- Current solution: {current_solution_they_use}\n\n**SEQUENCE STRUCTURE:**\n\n**Email 1 â€” Day 0 (Framework: Problem-Agitate-Solve)**\n- Subject: Max 5 words, lowercase, curiosity-driven\n- Preview text: 40 chars, complements subject\n- Body: 4 sentences max. Open with {{prospect_company}} specific observation.\n- CTA: Soft â€” "Worth a quick look?"\n\n**Email 2 â€” Day 3 (Framework: Before-After-Bridge)**\n- Subject: Reply to thread OR new angle\n- Body: Share a specific case study: "{{similar_company}} was {before_state}. After switching, {after_state} in {timeframe}."\n- CTA: "Can I share how?"\n\n**Email 3 â€” Day 7 (Framework: Social Proof)**\n- Subject: Use a number/metric\n- Body: Lead with ROI stat. Name-drop 2-3 recognisable customers.\n- Include: "{metric_proof}" (e.g., "reduced churn by 34%")\n- CTA: Calendar link â€” "15 min this week?"\n\n**Email 4 â€” Day 12 (Framework: Value-Add Breakup)**\n- Subject: "resource for {{prospect_first_name}}"\n- Body: Share a genuinely useful resource (blog, framework, calculator)\n- Subtle mention of product. No hard sell.\n- CTA: "Found this useful for teams like yours"\n\n**Email 5 â€” Day 18 (Framework: Permission-Based Close)**\n- Subject: "closing the loop"\n- Body: 2 sentences. "Should I close your file or is this still relevant?"\n- CTA: Binary choice â€” "Reply 1 for yes, 2 for not now"\n\n**RULES:**\n- No "I hope this email finds you well"\n- No "I/We" in first sentence of any email\n- Every email under 80 words\n- Merge tags: {{prospect_first_name}}, {{prospect_company}}, {{prospect_title}}\n- Test deliverability: no spam trigger words',
  'Marketing', 'ChatGPT', 'intermediate', false,
  ARRAY['cold-email', 'saas', 'b2b', 'outreach', 'drip-campaign', 'sales'],
  245, 1576, 5900, NOW()
),

