(
  'Epic Fantasy Battle Scene with Volumetric Lighting (SDXL)',
  'Generate a hyper-detailed fantasy battle illustration optimised for SDXL with specific LoRA suggestions, controlnet poses, and negative prompts. For game concept artists and fantasy illustrators.',
  E'Generate an epic fantasy battle scene with cinematic composition:\n\n**SCENE COMPOSITION:**\n- Foreground: {foreground_character} in dynamic {action_pose}, wearing {armor_description}\n- Midground: Clash between {faction_a} and {faction_b} armies\n- Background: {environment} with {atmospheric_effect}\n- Camera: Low-angle hero shot, Dutch tilt 15Â°\n\n**CHARACTER DETAIL:**\n- Race/species: {character_race}\n- Weapon: {weapon_type} with {magical_effect} enchantment\n- Expression: {emotion} â€” showing determination and battle fury\n- Armor material: {material} with battle damage and scratches\n\n**LIGHTING:**\n- Primary: Volumetric god rays from {light_source_position}\n- Secondary: {magical_color} magical glow emanating from weapon\n- Ambient: Warm firelight from burning structures\n- Atmosphere: Dust particles, ember sparks, smoke wisps\n\n**COLOR PALETTE:**\n- Dominant: {dominant_color}\n- Accent: {accent_color} (magical elements)\n- Shadows: Deep {shadow_tone}\n\n**TECHNICAL PARAMETERS:**\n- Style: {art_style} (e.g., Greg Rutkowski, Craig Mullins, Feng Zhu)\n- Quality tags: masterpiece, best quality, ultra detailed, 8k, sharp focus\n- Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras\n- CFG Scale: 7-9\n- Steps: 30-50\n\n**NEGATIVE PROMPT:**\nlow quality, blurry, deformed hands, extra fingers, bad anatomy, watermark, text, signature, cropped, worst quality, jpeg artifacts, duplicate, morbid, mutilated, poorly drawn face\n\n**SUGGESTED LoRAs:**\n- Detail enhancer LoRA (weight 0.6)\n- Fantasy armor LoRA (weight 0.5)\n- Epic lighting LoRA (weight 0.7)',
  'Design', 'Stable Diffusion', 'intermediate', false,
  ARRAY['fantasy', 'battle-scene', 'sdxl', 'concept-art', 'game-art', 'illustration'],
  267, 1234, 4100, NOW()
),

