(
  'Programmatic SEO Content Brief with NLP Entity Targeting',
  'Generate a data-driven content brief that targets specific NLP entities, includes TF-IDF keyword mapping, SERP intent analysis, and internal linking strategy. For SEO teams scaling content production.',
  E'You are a senior SEO strategist specialising in programmatic content at scale (1,000+ pages/month).\n\nCreate a comprehensive content brief for the target keyword: "{primary_keyword}"\n\n**KEYWORD RESEARCH:**\n- Primary keyword: {primary_keyword}\n- Estimated monthly search volume: {search_volume}\n- Keyword difficulty: {kd_score}/100\n- CPC: ${cpc}\n- Search intent: {intent_type} (informational/commercial/transactional/navigational)\n\n**SERP ANALYSIS:**\nAnalyse the current top 5 results and identify:\n1. Content format (listicle, guide, comparison, tool)\n2. Average word count of ranking pages\n3. Common H2/H3 headings across results\n4. Content gaps (topics top results miss)\n5. Featured snippet opportunity type\n\n**CONTENT BRIEF:**\n\n1. **Meta Title:** {50-60 chars, keyword-front-loaded}\n2. **Meta Description:** {150-160 chars, includes CTA}\n3. **URL Slug:** /{optimised_slug}\n4. **Target Word Count:** {word_count} words\n5. **Content Type:** {content_format}\n\n6. **OUTLINE (H2/H3 structure):**\n   - H1: {title}\n   - H2: {section_1} [target: {lsi_keyword_1}]\n     - H3: {subsection}\n   - H2: {section_2} [target: {lsi_keyword_2}]\n   - ... (minimum 6 H2 sections)\n\n7. **NLP ENTITIES TO INCLUDE:**\n   List 15-20 entities Google expects in content about this topic:\n   | Entity | Type | Prominence (1-3) |\n\n8. **TF-IDF KEYWORD MAP:**\n   | Keyword | Target Frequency | Current Top-Page Avg |\n   (Include 20+ LSI keywords)\n\n9. **INTERNAL LINKING:**\n   - Pages to link TO from this content: {internal_links}\n   - Pages that should link BACK to this content: {backlink_sources}\n\n10. **SCHEMA MARKUP:** Recommend appropriate schema (FAQ, HowTo, Article)\n\n11. **VISUAL ASSETS NEEDED:**\n    - Custom graphics: {list}\n    - Screenshots: {list}\n    - Data visualizations: {list}\n\n12. **COMPETITOR CONTENT TO BEAT:**\n    - URL: {competitor_url}\n    - Their word count: {word_count}\n    - What they do well:\n    - What they miss (our opportunity):\n\nNiche: {niche}\nWebsite domain: {domain}',
  'Content Writing', 'ChatGPT', 'advanced', false,
  ARRAY['seo', 'content-brief', 'programmatic-seo', 'nlp', 'keyword-research'],
  389, 2456, 8800, NOW()
),

-- â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
