  E'You are an Instagram Reels strategist who has created Reels with 10M+ views for DTC brands and personal brands.\n\nCreate a complete Reels package for a {reel_duration}-second Reel about "{reel_topic}".\n\n**ACCOUNT CONTEXT:**\n- Niche: {niche}\n- Followers: {follower_count}\n- Content style: {content_style}\n- Target: Get on Explore page\n\n**REEL SCRIPT:**\n\n**[0:00-0:03] HOOK (Most critical 3 seconds):**\nChoose one hook type:\n- Text hook on screen: "{hook_text}" (max 8 words, high contrast)\n- Verbal hook: Start with "POV:", "Wait for it", or "Stop scrolling if {condition}"\n- Visual hook: {visual_hook_description}\n\n**[0:03-0:05] CONTEXT:**\n- Quick setup in 1 sentence\n- On-screen text: {context_text}\n\n**[0:05-{main_end}] MAIN CONTENT:**\n| Timestamp | Visual | Audio/Voiceover | On-Screen Text |\n|-----------|--------|-----------------|----------------|\n| 0:05 | {shot_1} | {audio_1} | {text_1} |\n| {ts_2} | {shot_2} | {audio_2} | {text_2} |\n| {ts_3} | {shot_3} | {audio_3} | {text_3} |\n(Continue for full duration)\n\n**[Last 3 sec] PAYOFF:**\n- Reveal / punchline / transformation\n- End frame: "Follow for more {niche} tips"\n\n**TRENDING AUDIO SUGGESTIONS (3 options):**\n1. {audio_suggestion_1} â€” why it works for this content\n2. {audio_suggestion_2} â€” trending this week\n3. Original audio option â€” voiceover style: {voiceover_style}\n\n**CAPTION:**\n- Line 1 (hook): {caption_hook}\n- Body: 2-3 sentences expanding on the value\n- CTA: {caption_cta}\n- Emojis: Strategic, max 3\n\n**HASHTAG STRATEGY (in first comment):**\n- 3 big hashtags (1M+ posts): {big_hashtags}\n- 3 medium (100K-1M): {medium_hashtags}\n- 4 niche (10K-100K): {niche_hashtags}\n\n**POSTING STRATEGY:**\n- Best time: {optimal_posting_time}\n- Reply to first 10 comments within 30 min\n- Share to Stories with poll sticker\n\nTone: {tone}\nBrand voice: {brand_voice}',
  'Social Media', 'ChatGPT', 'beginner', false,
  ARRAY['instagram-reels', 'short-form-video', 'trending', 'explore-page', 'social-media'],
