  E'You are a design systems architect who has built systems at companies like Shopify (Polaris), GitHub (Primer), and Atlassian (Atlassian Design System).\n\nCreate a comprehensive component specification for the {component_name} component.\n\n**COMPONENT OVERVIEW:**\n- Name: {component_name}\n- Category: {category} (e.g., Data Display, Navigation, Input, Feedback)\n- Design system: {system_name}\n- Framework: {framework} (React/Vue/Svelte/Web Components)\n\n**1. ANATOMY:**\nDescribe each sub-element:\n| Element | Required | Description |\n|---------|----------|-------------|\n| {root} | Yes | Container element |\n| {element_1} | Yes/No | Description |\n| {element_2} | | |\n\n**2. VARIANTS:**\n| Variant | Use Case | Visual Difference |\n|---------|----------|-------------------|\n| {variant_1} | {when_to_use} | {visual_diff} |\n| {variant_2} | | |\n| {variant_3} | | |\n\n**3. DESIGN TOKENS:**\n```json\n{\n  "{component_name}": {\n    "border-radius": "{radius_token}",\n    "padding": "{spacing_token}",\n    "font-size": "{typography_token}",\n    "color-background": "{color_token}",\n    "color-text": "{color_token}",\n    "shadow": "{elevation_token}",\n    "transition": "{motion_token}"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**4. INTERACTION STATES:**\n| State | Visual Change | Token Override |\n|-------|--------------|----------------|\n| Default | | |\n| Hover | | |\n| Focus | 2px ring, offset 2px | focus-ring-color |\n| Active/Pressed | | |\n| Disabled | opacity 0.4, cursor not-allowed | |\n| Loading | | |\n| Error | | |\n\n**5. ACCESSIBILITY (WCAG 2.2 AA):**\n- Role: {aria_role}\n- ARIA attributes: {aria_attributes}\n- Keyboard navigation:\n  | Key | Action |\n  |-----|--------|\n  | Tab | {action} |\n  | Enter/Space | {action} |\n  | Escape | {action} |\n  | Arrow keys | {action} |\n- Color contrast: {contrast_ratio} (minimum 4.5:1 for text)\n- Screen reader announcement: "{announcement_text}"\n- Focus management: {focus_behavior}\n\n**6. RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR:**\n| Breakpoint | Behavior |\n|------------|----------|\n| Mobile (<640px) | {behavior} |\n| Tablet (640-1024px) | {behavior} |\n| Desktop (>1024px) | {behavior} |\n\n**7. CODE API:**\n```typescript\ninterface {ComponentName}Props {\n  /** {description} */\n  variant?: {variant_union_type};\n  /** {description} */\n  size?: ''sm'' | ''md'' | ''lg'';\n  /** {description} */\n  disabled?: boolean;\n  /** {description} */\n  children: React.ReactNode;\n  /** Callback fired on {event} */\n  on{Event}?: (event: {EventType}) => void;\n}\n```\n\n**8. USAGE GUIDELINES:**\n- DO: {best_practice_1}\n- DO: {best_practice_2}\n- DON''T: {anti_pattern_1}\n- DON''T: {anti_pattern_2}\n\n**9. RELATED COMPONENTS:**\n- Use {related_1} instead when {condition}\n- Combine with {related_2} for {pattern}',
