nder/on-track}\n\n**5. WEEKLY REVIEW TEMPLATE (for Friday):**\n- What got done? (vs. planned)\n- What didn''t? Why?\n- Key learning this week:\n- Adjustment for next week:\n- Gratitude/win:',
